newsitem.title: EU: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 293 OF NOVEMBER 16, 1996.
newsitem.headline: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 293 OF NOVEMBER 16, 1996.

text.p: (Note - contents are displayed in reverse order to that in the printed Journal)
COUNCIL DECISION of 11 November 1996 appointing three members and two alternate members of the Committee of the Regions (96/646/EC)
COUNCIL DECISION of 11 November 1996 appointing a member of the Economic and Social Committee (96/645/Euratom, EC)
COUNCIL DECISION of 11 November 1996 on the extension of the legal protection of topographies of semiconductor products to persons from the Isle of Man (96/644/EC)
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2199/96 of 15 November 1996 determining the world market price for unginned cotton and the rate for the aid
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2198/96 of 15 November 1996 fixing the import duties in the cereals sector
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2197/96 of 15 November 1996 establishing the standard import values for determining the entry price of certain fruit and vegetables
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2196/96 of 15 November 1996 setting export refunds on fruit and vegetables

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2195/96 of 15 November 1996 fixing the maximum buying-in price and the quantities of beef to be bought in under the 171st partial invitation to tender as a general intervention measure pursuant to Regulations (EEC) No 1627/89 and (EC) No 2002/96

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2194/96 of 15 November 1996 amending Regulation (EEC) No 120/89 laying down common detailed rules for the application of export levies and charges on agricultural products

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2193/96 of 15 November 1996 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2131/93 laying down the procedure and conditions for the sale of cereals held by intervention agencies END OF DOCUMENT.
